title: Live with Comfort & Luxury in this Spacious 3-Bedroom Home!
posting_body: ['It is time to get out of a cramped, noisy apartment and into a home of your own!', 'The first step is to give us a call!', 'Our New Home Consultants are ready to help you pick out your new home and go through out easy, step-by-step process!', ' Come see this stunning 3 bedrooms and 2 bath Pecos floor plan home.', 'This is a popular one story home loaded with upgrades and features a modern kitchen, spacious living room and a flex room with French doors!', 'This spacious home is located only minutes from Tomball.', ' Make an appointment now and visit this beautiful community that features a beautiful park with a splashpad, walking trails and a playground.', 'Pecos Floor Plan', '3 Bedrooms', '2 Bathrooms', 'Study/Flex room', 'Breakfast Room', '2 Car Garage', 'show contact info', 'ext 300', 'Only $1379/month*', 'With our help, the dream of homeownership is possible!', 'Call now!', 'show contact info', 'ext 300', '* P & I. Price $290,900, 5.875% Fixed / 6.746% APR, 20% Down, CONV 30 Year OAC from third party lender.', 'Other fees such as taxes, insurance and HOA are not included in the sample monthly payment amount.', 'Prices and rates are subject to change without notice.']
